Package.JSON
> All Meta Data 
    > Description, name, version ,author
> All package we use
> Script 
    > start
    > Testing

///////////////////////
Step to generate package.JSON
/////////////////////
** NodeJs must be installed in system
> Go inside the folder where you want to generate using cmd/terminal
> type npm init 
> answer all question
> type "yes"

--------------------------------
How to install packages
-----------------------------
Local dependency   > local to folder
Dev dependency     > local and use only at time of development
global dependency   


///////////////////////
Step to install Local dependency 
/////////////////////
** NodeJs must be installed in system
> Go inside the folder where you want to generate using cmd/terminal
> npm i packagename

///////////////////////
Step to install Local dependency 
/////////////////////
** NodeJs must be installed in system
> Go inside the folder where you want to generate using cmd/terminal
> npm i packagename --save-dev

