https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community


function add(a,b){
    return a+b
}

add(1,2)


//////
step to setup mongodb
/////

> download mongodb
> install
> create one folder in c drive by name of data 
> inside data folder create db folder 

>>>>>>
Step to run mongodb
<<<<<<<
open cmd
> go inside folder
> c:\programmfile\mongodb\server\4.4\bin 
> type mongod  (it will start the mongodb server)
    (port => 27017)

> open new cmd
> c:\programmfile\mongodb\server\4.4\bin 
> type mongo (it will start the mongodb cli)


